lead_paragraph: Charles Woodson said he felt "good" about retiring, even though the final act for the Oakland strong safety ended in disappointment when the Raiders lost 23-17 to the playoff-bound Kansas City Chiefs on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Woodson Bows Out With a Loss After Long and Storied Career
